Params: {3: 'The battle quickly finished. Peace returns to the church.'}
{3: 'Toby is struggling to get on his feet. "Blood" keeps coming out of his "wounds", but he is still smiling.'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Toby', 3: 'Something different is happening to me. If only I could die easily like others...', 4: '1'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Bianca', 3: "Don't apologize. It's my bad... I couldn't save you...", 4: '1'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Toby', 3: 'No... You did. Maybe you have also saved others...', 4: '1'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Toby', 3: "I'm glad that I met you in the end...", 4: '1'}
{3: "After finishing the last line, Toby's legs can no longer hold him up."}
{3: 'Toby falls into his own blood and calmly closes his eyes under the moon.'}
{3: 'A lily flower slips out of his arms and falls to the ground, soaked in the red liquid.'}
{3: "Toby's last words still linger in her mind, but his cold body reminds her of reality."}
{1: '1', 2: 'Bianca', 3: 'Why... Why do you all trust me so much? Father, and you...', 4: '1'}
{2: 'Bianca', 3: 'You talked about redemption and relief. But you are all dead!', 4: '1'}
{3: "Bianca's thoughts are interrupted by the sudden screaming. She looks over and sees an unexpected guest at the front door."}
{3: 'The terrified Sister rushes out, leaving no chance for Bianca to get close. Soon, many voices can be heard from all directions...'}
